## Applied (safe, surgical — high-frequency failures from improvements.md)
1. `.claude/agents/demo-builder.md` self-test: added a hard **dash gate**
   (`grep -rl $'[–—]' demo-src/src index.html` must be empty, incl `<title>`/meta)
   and a **live-data gate** (curl every hero/supporting endpoint, assert real
   non-empty data, never label mock/fallback as "Live" without an offline badge).
   Sources: ~6 build-ceo notes (dashes shipped 3-4 passes; weather 502 masked by mock).
2. `.claude/agents/proposal-writer.md`: replaced the per-file dash grep with ONE
   repo-wide grep across ALL deliverables for literal U+2014/2013 AND HTML entities
   (`&mdash;`/`&ndash;`/`&#8212;`/`&#8211;`). Source: final-ceo (writer only fixed footer entity).
3. `.claude/agents/deploy-test.md`: added Flask-shape early `/health` check (catch
   managed-service/blueprint interception before full Playwright), an infinite-API-
   loop named test case (>10 identical reqs in 5s), and two-phase auth testing via
   `page.route()` header injection. Sources: 2 deploy-test improve-pass notes.
4. `CLAUDE.md` (new "Node service scaffold gotchas"): default to `node:sqlite`
   (better-sqlite3 gyp fails on Node22 Win) and avoid manual `Accept-Encoding` with
   node-fetch v2 (brotli "Invalid response body" → 502); prefer global fetch.
   Sources: demo-builder + build-ceo reuse notes (both caused mid-run fix scripts).

